Cell["\<\
The fully-contracted terms processed henceforth correspond to \
fully-contracted diagonally-and-antidiagonally-dressed disjoint Bogoliubov \
contributions generated by the application of Wick\[CloseCurlyQuote]s theorem \
to the following matrix element (cf. expansion formula of Gorkov\
\[CloseCurlyQuote]s polarization propagator), \
\>", "Text",
