Cell["\<\
Loading of the 96 (48 and 16) input sequences of single particle indices, \
corresponding to diagonally-and-antidiagonally-dressed Bogoliubov Feynman \
diagrams of disjoint type with three (two and one)distinct one-body vertices.\
